sentences: John Samels, better known by his stage name Paper Tiger, is a hip hop producer and DJ from Minneapolis, Minnesota, who is currently based in Brooklyn, New York.
Paper Tiger released the 7-inch vinyl single, Cloquet, in December 2009.
His first solo album, Made Like Us, was released in July 2010.
